flowchart LR
    START["Run start"] --> T1["@task A complete
checkpoint saved"] --> T2["@task B running"] --> FAIL["worker crash / timeout"]
    FAIL --> RESTORE["Load last checkpoint"] --> RESUME["Resume from task B boundary"] --> T3["remaining tasks"] --> END["Final result"]
    T2 -. side effects must be idempotent .-> FAIL

